column5: A few small smallies, a couple of followers, 2 missed fish (operator error?   ) and a nice 21" largemouth on a wacky Yum dinger
thanks...she can't wait to get in the boat-as soon as you go near the dock in she jumps
gotta love it when a dog is just as ready as you are to go in the boat to go fishing!
Nice fish and a great boat partner!
